{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"urj8q1uq98o3upmgbt2qxns","title":"Troubleshoot","desc":"","updated":1671014275336,"created":1671014275336,"custom":{},"fname":"troubleshoot","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Harshita-notes","sync":"sync"},"contentHash":"3e6b2ed71ca1a614f7795138d90183df","links":[],"anchors":{"kill-a-port":{"type":"header","text":"kill a port","value":"kill-a-port","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"npm-connection-refused-error":{"type":"header","text":"npm connection refused error","value":"npm-connection-refused-error","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"prettier-not-working-on-save":{"type":"header","text":"prettier not working on save?","value":"prettier-not-working-on-save","line":25,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"dlb5bmx7v8f6otsgongz4vx","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"troubleshoot\">Troubleshoot<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#troubleshoot\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"kill-a-port\">kill a port<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kill-a-port\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">\n<span class=\"token function\">netstat</span> -ano <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> findstr :3000\n\ntaskkill /PID <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span>PID<span class=\"token operator\">></span> /F\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"npm-connection-refused-error\">npm connection refused error<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#npm-connection-refused-error\"></a></h2>\n<pre><code>npm config set proxy null\nnpm config set https-proxy null\nnpm config set registry http://registry.npmjs.org/\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"prettier-not-working-on-save\">prettier not working on save?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#prettier-not-working-on-save\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>go to settings: > cmd+shidt+P/Ctrl + Shift+P > Preferences: Open Settings (UI) > write on save in search bar, check Editor: Format on Save</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"dlb5bmx7v8f6otsgongz4vx","title":"Hi","desc":"","updated":1663067414354,"created":1648190029829,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Harshita-notes","sync":"sync"},"contentHash":"d82c7b00722ccf7feb590e2be8038e07","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"dlb5bmx7v8f6otsgongz4vx","vaultName":"Harshita-notes"},"value":"user.tharshita13","alias":"@tharshita13","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":12,"offset":647},"end":{"line":17,"column":24,"offset":659},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"user.tharshita13"}}],"anchors":{"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["trkx8xrg7g2fm023ez4ldqj","c8csxid3zoghxorepwcrami","urj8q1uq98o3upmgbt2qxns","biwq9kqwuqpvhl1toq66fl7","2fh3ebwzm9hp76pcigmxlut","x3hyndqfnjrucp7o49i9ykz","euxxrq5wtmvwtqf09izx90g"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nHi,\nWelcome to Harshita's Digital Garden 🌱\nI'm Harshita Joshi. I'm a software engineer who also has a passion for teaching.\nWhen not at the computer, I play ukulele, do yoga, study [German](https://harshita-mindfire.github.io/german-for-beginners/) and wonder about having numerous pets.\n\nEven though I don't travel very often, I try to capture the city's charm through photographs. Click [here](https://harshita-mindfire.github.io/) to see a glimpse of my gallery.\n\n## Contacts\n\nYou can find and contact me in the following places\n\n- Email: tharshita13@gmail.com\n\n- Github: [Harshita-mindfire](https://github.com/Harshita-mindfire)\n\n- Medium: [@tharshita13](https://medium.com/@tharshita13)\n\n- LinkedIn: [Harshita Joshi](https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshita-joshi-030b29118/)\n\n- Instagram: [imharshita07](https://www.instagram.com/imharshita07/)\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults"